title: Keegan Swenson Delivers for Team USA with Fifth at the UCI Gravel World Championships
content:
Swenson clawed out of a bad start position to race in the front all day, chase back after a crash, and sprint Alejandro Valverde to the line.

Read the full article at Keegan Swenson Delivers for Team USA with Fifth at the UCI Gravel World Championships on Velo.
author: Betsy Welch
